name: IRIS AI
description: IRIS AI is a fully autonomous AI that connects to your wallet, understands your trading style, and makes smart, real-time decisions across DeFi — while you sleep. It uses sophisticated algorithms to identify emerging opportunities and manage risk 24/7. It doesn’t send alerts — it takes action. To get started, simply create an account on irissai.com, connect your wallet, and explore the onboarding guide. You'll be guided through setting up strategies, choosing risk profiles, and activating your AI agent.
